'''Ferals''' were beings of many [[Species/Legends|species]] living in the [[Coruscant Underworld/Legends|Coruscant underworld]]. They were the savage descendants of those who had been surviving there since the [[Terraforming/Legends|terraforming]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].

Many were controlled by the [[World Brain]] and also spied on the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothans]] for [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]]. After the death of the World Brain, the Ferals began to take control of their base instincts once more.

